com.feilong.servlet.http.entity

Class RequestLogSwitch

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.feilong.servlet.http.entity.RequestLogSwitch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public abstract class RequestLogSwitch
extends Object
implements Serializable
    request log显示开关.

    These classes are intended to be used as Singletons. There is no need to instantiate a new style each time. A program will generally use one of the predefined constants on this class.

    默认显示:

    • showFullURL 请求路径
    • showMethod 提交方法
    • showParams 参数

    借鉴了 ToStringStyle 的思想

    readResolve()方法:

    一般来说, 一个类实现了 Serializable接口, 我们就可以把它往内存地写再从内存里读出而"组装"成一个跟原来一模一样的对象.
    不过当序列化遇到单例时,这里边就有了个问题: 从内存读出而组装的对象破坏了单例的规则.
    单例是要求一个JVM中只有一个类对象的,而现在通过反序列化,一个新的对象克隆了出来.

    Since:
    1.4.0
    Author:
    feilong
    See Also:
    ToStringStyle, Serialized Form
